                INSERT INTO project (project_id, project_name)
                VALUES (
                    $1,
                    'My Project'
                )
            ),
            insert_warehouse AS (
                INSERT INTO warehouse (warehouse_id, warehouse_name, project_id, status, "tabular_delete_mode")
                VALUES (
                    $2,

                    'active',

                attempt,
                warehouse_id,
                queue_name,
                task_data,
                status,
                entity_id,
                entity_name,
                entity_type,
                project_id,
                attempt_scheduled_for,
                task_created_at,
                created_at
            )
            VALUES
            (
                $3,
                1,
                $2,
                'old_task',
                '{}',
                'success',
                NULL,
                NULL,
                'warehouse',
                $1,
                now() - make_interval(days => ($5 + 10)),
                now() - make_interval(days => ($5 + 10)),
                now() - make_interval(days => ($5 + 10))
            ),
            (
                $4,
                1,
                $2,
                'recent_task',
                '{}',
                'success',
                NULL,
                NULL,
                'warehouse',
                $1,
                now() - make_interval(days => ($5 - 10)),

            )
